Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.30,0:00:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 卡萊多之星要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.20,0:00:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家觀看時請注意保持室內明亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.20,0:00:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.50,0:00:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那麼 那麼 我是洛吉特哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.00,0:00:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看過我的空中飛人表演了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.80,0:00:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同心儀已久的偶像空一起表演 真是開心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要進行同空一樣的大特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.80,0:00:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得更加厲害給你們看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.10,0:00:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的應該是去挑戰空中飛人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.80,0:00:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就在那時 遇到了某個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.70,0:00:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.30,0:00:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這次也要進行精彩的演出 演出 演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.60,0:02:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.80,0:02:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆那裏我也打過招呼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.50,0:02:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我和媽媽約好了 所以要先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有八張機票 給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝 可是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那兒之後的行程也在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.30,0:02:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 但是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 法國見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法國……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.80,0:02:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.80,0:02:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.70,0:02:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她媽媽安娜出面擔保才能得到的機會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.20,0:03:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯納斯汽車展的表演引起了很大的鬥志啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.50,0:03:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是安娜提出的以表演空竹作為參加的條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.40,0:03:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才在一周前她就出發了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.50,0:03:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正對我們小丑小組來說 這是夢寐以求的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.10,0:03:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.80,0:03:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我作為這次活動的負責人……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.20,0:03:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬戲節之後的再次來法國啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.70,0:03:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定以笑容面對法國啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.80,0:03:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 打擾一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.60,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還呆在那兒瞎說什麼啊 快走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.40,0:03:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話還是那麼沖……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.70,0:03:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找計程車的話這邊走 反正是在市內吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過上次表演 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.90,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空一邊表演 一邊看著觀眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.10,0:03:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我卻一直只是看著空和雷恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.40,0:04:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空具有的能夠勝過我的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.50,0:04:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是能夠讓觀眾開心的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造出笑容的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.90,0:04:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要得到這種力量 首先要取回自己真正的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.50,0:04:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是蕾拉想要告訴我的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,\h\h\h\h{\fnTahoma\b0}theatre\N{\r}那個……馬戲團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.80,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,\h\h\h\h{\fnTahoma\b0}nuwar\N{\r}那個……挪威爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,\h{\fnTahoma\b0}oui\h \h \hmadmadame\N{\r}我知道了 可愛的女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 看來他明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,\h\h\h\h{\fnTahoma\b0}theatre\N{\r}那個……馬戲團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,\h\h\h\h{\fnTahoma\b0}nuwar\N{\r}那個……挪威爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 快起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.70,0:04:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人來了 睡覺可不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,\h{\fnTahoma\b0}oui \h\h oui \h\h oui \h\h madmadame\N{\r}知道 知道 知道了 女士！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.80,0:04:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎到 諾阿魯馬戲團 羅傑特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家也應該很快就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他們來之前讓我在這裏等可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 在明天開始的表演中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.50,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以稍微的加入空竹表演嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.70,0:05:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話要另外加錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.40,0:05:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的合約是以出演空中飛人角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級巨星苗木野空和這次馬戲節的優勝者梅出場的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.10,0:05:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我則是普通的雜技演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊……我明白了、明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.50,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的話就當我沒說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然還不熟練 但我會努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力不讓團長和觀眾失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我們的明星魯內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.30,0:05:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 漂亮的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態不錯啊 魯內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是像平常一樣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼生氣 我馬上就走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.00,0:06:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說不會再來這裏的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.80,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷淡啊 我好歹是你的師傅啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.00,0:06:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是你的徒弟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是稍微手頭有點緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.60,0:06:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是買酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.70,0:06:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是瞭解我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.10,0:06:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.30,0:06:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉啊 我一定會還給你的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用還了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.20,0:06:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不再出現在我面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.10,0:06:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,\h\h\h\h\h{\fnTahoma\b0}au revoir\N{\r}真是大方啊 拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.80,0:06:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.90,0:06:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭‧努萬 曾經是有名的空中飛人訓練員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中飛人的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.70,0:07:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭以前是自由訓練員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.60,0:07:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那些將來很有希望的孩子培養成一流的空中飛人演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.00,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個魯內也曾經是他的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.70,0:07:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上他這樣的教練可說是世界上屈指可數的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.10,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾年前突然不幹了 現在就是你看到的這個樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.50,0:07:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上屈指可數的教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？喂……羅傑特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.70,0:07:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡萊多劇團的羅傑特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我空中飛人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想現在就能飛起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.60,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多的人嗎 好慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.00,0:07:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演不是明天才……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.50,0:07:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再說什麼啊 快點來開始排練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直跟著我也是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.30,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你教我之前我是不會放棄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬戲的練習場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只是個破爛的倉庫罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以蕩鞦韆嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 這個真漂亮啊……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.20,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你這樣的外行都能加入 卡萊多劇團也不行了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.40,0:09:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看卡萊多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.10,0:09:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中飛人是我自己想練而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.10,0:09:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有這樣的技術……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.20,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.50,0:09:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒聽說還要這樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呀 這可是我們的拿手好戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？！怎麼這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.40,0:09:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.30,0:10:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈～太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這樣的馬戲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是明星節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.70,0:10:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問這裏是不是挪威爾瑪戲團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.40,0:10:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好表演的卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.20,0:10:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為沒命了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.40,0:10:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很有趣嗎？又驚險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.30,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎到來 一直在等你們哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.20,0:10:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們遲到了 我們是卡萊多劇團的出巡小組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.40,0:10:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特還沒來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可能在阿蘭那裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.60,0:10:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 已經準備放棄了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.10,0:10:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不放棄 空在萊恩的特訓下也是毫不示弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.10,0:10:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這點……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.00,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.90,0:11:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說萊恩‧奧斯瓦爾多嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你認識他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在在卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道雷恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.50,0:11:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.00,0:11:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我最後一個徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.20,0:11:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTahoma\b0}bonjour　　　　　\h　\h　\N{\r}您好 請問有人在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.80,0:11:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊恩在這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.50,0:11:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 已經是10年前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.50,0:11:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊恩和妹妹索菲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們很早就失去了雙親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.70,0:11:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被寄養在親戚家裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.20,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和親戚的關係不是很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想收養他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的養父母立刻答應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.80,0:12:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個都是優秀的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.10,0:12:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本的鞦韆上的技巧很快就掌握了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.50,0:12:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩 把索菲直接扔起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.90,0:12:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.80,0:12:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲擁有能夠成為雷恩搭檔的能力嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.30,0:12:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 不 不如說萊恩沒有能夠成為索菲搭檔的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說比萊恩還厲害？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.00,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是索菲的話 可能可以完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的天使的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.40,0:12:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的絕技？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.10,0:12:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.90,0:13:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為想要完成天使的絕技 就必須有搭檔的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先要把萊恩進行徹底的訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.90,0:13:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法啊 來 給……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.30,0:13:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？這個球是什麼啊！灌了鉛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無論怎麼訓練雷恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.90,0:13:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的絕技總是無法成型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.30,0:13:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始想是不是萊恩不行的時候 發生了那件事……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.40,0:13:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.90,0:13:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲就好像羽毛那麼輕巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將自己托了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了那個我就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.10,0:13:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的絕技不僅僅需要拍檔的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.20,0:13:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更需要的是擁有天生的感悟力的充滿演繹力量的表演者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.10,0:14:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我更確信能完美實現天使的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.10,0:14:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對索菲開始了嚴厲的特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲 不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退錢……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲實在太累了 沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.50,0:14:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呀 你們是為了讓我們開心才在這裏的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太傲慢了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.10,0:14:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就不能給出場費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再進行特訓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.70,0:14:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去索菲會吃不消的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.90,0:14:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 萊恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.30,0:14:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲！但是你……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道真正的明星嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的明星？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.90,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以前的馬戲明星告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.50,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於將所有人的心融合成一顆心的真正的明星的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.40,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得天使的絕技可能就是成為真正的明星的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.00,0:15:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩 我想試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.70,0:15:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成天使的絕技 成為真正的明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.50,0:15:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些看到的人 觀眾也好 演員也好 所有的心融合成一顆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.60,0:15:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感受到溫暖 好像一家人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的絕技是能讓人成為真正的明星的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.70,0:15:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我知道我的目標是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.90,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使要賭上我這一生 也要使天使的絕技在我的手中完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.00,0:15:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠培育出天使的只有惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.30,0:15:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了在馬戲團時聽到的一句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力以天使的絕技為目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.80,0:15:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓越來越難以接受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個特訓……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.90,0:16:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我在馬戲節前接受的特訓一樣……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.30,0:16:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.10,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個樣子你以為就能完成天使的絕技嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.20,0:16:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要走是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.90,0:16:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經從你這裏學不到什麼東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.30,0:16:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的天使的絕技我會來完成它的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓索菲成為真正的明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只不過是我的墊腳石罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能辦得到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能成為真正的惡魔嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾年後當我聽說索菲的死訊的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.40,0:16:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想就此消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩有這樣的過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.90,0:17:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前還以為雷恩的特訓只是要毀了空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.80,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是有意義的啊……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.90,0:17:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的絕技是通往真正的明星的道路？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.40,0:17:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 所謂的真正的明星什麼的那是個夢幻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.50,0:17:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不恨 誰也不怨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.80,0:17:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能成為明星的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.90,0:17:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使天使的絕技完全成功也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 並不是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得真正的明星是完全能夠實現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.90,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的絕技的背後 有著通向真正明星的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲小姐是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.80,0:17:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我完美的天使的絕技吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.90,0:17:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我已經不相信這些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要靠你的腿一步一步自己走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.50,0:17:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要是三年前遇見你 也許我還會相信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.20,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特 還要繼續練習嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.60,0:18:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 把無聊的故事放到一邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.40,0:18:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的眼神 到現在為止從沒見過 如此的充滿鬥志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.30,0:18:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向真正的卡萊多之星的路終於被我發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要順著這條路走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.30,0:18:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論花多少時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.20,0:18:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為真正的卡萊多之星！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作一定要與鞦韆的保持一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.20,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何要一定要看清三秒前飛過來的鞦韆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三秒之後的鞦韆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.10,0:18:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.40,0:18:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太得意了 要進入下一個環節了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.80,0:18:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一天就可以了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.60,0:19:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謀害公主的壞人就是我的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.80,0:19:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣 哼哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.40,0:19:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼我要扮壞人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.40,0:19:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要剿滅惡魔 覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.00,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比上次動作幅度更大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的動作變得那麼生動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的演出我也感覺到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.70,0:19:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不僅僅是為了創造出客人的笑容的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.80,0:19:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知從何時起 她要提升自己演技的熱情不斷提高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.00,0:19:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是空真正的實力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.10,0:20:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩的演技 可以帶動別人的情緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再不倒下的話時間就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要那樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.60,0:20:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅好像很開心的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會就這樣算了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅傑特 準備好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.70,0:21:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.80,0:21:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.90,0:21:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙著眼睛表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.70,0:21:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬戲節過了沒多久就能再次站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.20,0:21:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.80,0:21:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫空的演員不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.80,0:21:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你的體格看 你也是馬戲演員吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.10,0:21:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確那個演員有著不可思議的魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.40,0:21:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許她真的能讓「真正的明星」成為現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.70,0:21:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼認為嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.70,0:22:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你……好像在哪見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.00,0:22:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是由利‧凱力亞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.00,0:22:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團有什麼企圖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.10,0:22:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是很偉大的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.80,0:22:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 到底怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.00,0:22:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於找到了自己要走的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.70,0:22:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要完成完美的 天使的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.30,0:22:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天……一定會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.66,0:23:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告\N卡萊多之星 新生之翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.36,0:23:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你復仇的機會來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.21,0:23:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 卡萊多劇團回來了 但是..
